<header class="welcome-header">
  <h1 class="welcome-title">THE SHARED ECONOMY OF GARBAGE.</h1>
  <h2 class="welcome-subtitle animated fadeInUp">Buy & sell extra garbage space in a few clicks.</h2>
  <a style="text-align:center;" href="#newuser" class="btn animated fadeInUp">GET STARTED!</a>
  <a><%= image_tag 'downward-arrow.png', class:"downward-arrow", href:"#when-you-sell" %></a>
</header>

<div class="introduction">
  <%= image_tag 'money-bags.png', :width => 100, :height => 95, class:"garbage-bag" %>
  <p class="intro-line">
    We have saved buyers <strong>$1705.50</strong> since launch!
  </p>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="sell-container">
    <div class="when-you-sell animated fadeInLeft">
        <h2 class="when-you-title">When you sell!</h2>
        <%= image_tag 'money-bag.png',:width => 100, :height => 95, class:"money-bag", href:"money-bag"%>
      <ul class="when-you-sell-list">
        <li>
          If you've got extra space in your garbage, you can make money!
        </li>
        <br />
        <li>
          When you sell your garbage space, you and your fellow neighbours will both
          benifit! You're helping them save money, all the while you're making money!
          The less garbage you have come garbage day, could mean more money in your pocket!
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="buy-container" id="when-you-sell">
    <div class="when-you-buy animated fadeInRight">
      <h2 class="when-you-title">When you buy!</h2>
      <%= image_tag 'trash-bin-full.png',:width => 100, :height => 95, class:"trash-bin-full", href:"trash-bin-full"%>
      <ul class="when-you-sell-list">
        <li>
          See if your neighbours have extra space in their garbage and save money!
        </li>
        <br />
        <li >
          When you buy garbage space, you and your fellow neighbours will both
          benifit! Don't go out and buy extra bags! Save money by checking to see
          if your neighbours have extra garbage space. If so, buy it from them and save the hassle and money!
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> <!-- containter -->

<div class="intro-form">
  <div class="signup-container animated fadeInUp">
    <div id="newuser">
      <%= render 'users/form' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="login-container animated fadeInUp">
    <div id="login">
      <%= render 'sessions/form' %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
